{"tid":1842331,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(口罩)我發現連登仔太迷信VFE","createTime":"2020-01-25T15:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T16:15:29.000Z","uid":35420,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ff4d8939ec20aa2e44fd91559fe390d11b0688c7","tid":1842331,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:35:20.000Z","msg":"個個POST都問有冇VFE<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有D人仲話冇VFE冇用</span><br />\n但其實我諗好多人只係知呢幾個英文字母放係嘴邊UP<br />\n但詳情係乜黎根本冇理解過<br />\n<br />\n美國口罩用返美國標準 ASTM LEVEL1-3<br />\n3係最高但入面係冇VFE 呢樣野<br />\n咁係咪美國最高LEVEL標準既口罩對連登仔黎講都係廢?<br />\n<br />\n自己上網搵下VFE資料 全部都係日文<br />\n用VFE黎做唯一準則 <br />\n咁你所以美國口罩都可以唔需要買包括 3M既N95"},{"pid":"7a2f3f49adf5b9df756ef166d4344ea0ff52f4cc","tid":1842331,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a07d27f1b8c25e5260028359cb39f92699bbcf","tid":1842331,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:53:47.000Z","msg":"咁應該點睇隻口罩合唔合規格"},{"pid":"7e7b70afbfcb38fce1b4439aed51120ca3eeecdb","tid":1842331,"uid":344625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:54:39.000Z","msg":"樓主好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd047a78e9182a1d91df3f196084b0ff8204b022","tid":1842331,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6a07d27f1b8c25e5260028359cb39f92699bbcf","tid":1842331,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:53:47.000Z","msg":"咁應該點睇隻口罩合唔合規格"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:15:29.000Z","msg":"同問"}]}